with hedging, pruning, planting and de-thatching, we know how to help your garden keep up the shape!</p>\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title=\"Flowers &amp; Plants\"]</p>\n<p>Taking care of plants and flowers for both commercial and residential areas, we love to keep the world greener and tidier!</p>\n<p>As a team of experts, we\'re handy in working with absolutely any kind of plants, trees, and flowers.</p>\n<p>So whatever you\'ll need us to advise you or help you in regard to your garden, we\'ll be ready to do that at once!</p>\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title=\"Garden Design &amp; Landscaping\"]</p>\n<p>As landscape and exterior design firm we feel most comfortable working in spacious suburban areas...</p>\n<p>Additionally, the greenwalls installation makes up a big part of our urban landscaping services list.</p>\n<p>On par with that, commercial locations, such as offices or shopping malls use our greening services a lot.</p>\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item]</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_accordion][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_video admin_label=\"Video\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AuBnqBuV6i8\"]\n\n</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_video][tm_pb_video_slider admin_label=\"Video Slider\" show_image_overlay=\"hide\" show_arrows=\"on\" show_thumbnails=\"on\"]\n\n<p>\n[tm_pb_video_slider_item admin_title=\"Video\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5okJW7594zk\" image_src=\"http://hiryo2.local/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/img48.jpg\"]<br />[/tm_pb_video_slider_item][tm_pb_video_slider_item admin_title=\"Video\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7wAa2Y8CAIk\"]<br />[/tm_pb_video_slider_item][tm_pb_video_slider_item admin_title=\"Video\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LmIw9-TeOV4\"]<br />[/tm_pb_video_slider_item][tm_pb_video_slider_item admin_title=\"Video\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vf1UUzgGPto\"]<br />[/tm_pb_video_slider_item][tm_pb_video_slider_item admin_title=\"Video\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6a1zbt_R-dg\"]<br />[/tm_pb_video_slider_item]</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_video_slider][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section]', 'Elements', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'elements', '', '', '2016-09-23 07:30:45', '2016-09-23 07:30:45', '', 0, 'http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_58976-sample/?page_id=116', 0, 'page', '', 0);
